GLSL shader prorgams.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

default2d.glsl

    Simple, "all in one" shader program having
    both vertex and fragment shaders.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The rest are part of 3D shader family. New shader compilation system takes
in three groups of files: common, fragment and vertex. Common files are
combined with both shaders.

types.3d.glsl
default3d.in.glsl

    Common types and inputs for shaders.

verts.lib.glsl
frags.lib.glsl

    Function library for vertex and fragment shader.
    
verts.3d.glsl
frags.3d.glsl

    Vertex and fragment shader program main.
    
conf.toon3d.glsl

    Configuration files to get different behaviour.

